spirit:busInterface.spirit:description: axi lite interface for CAN core

spirit:component.spirit:description: The Xilinx CAN core solution is a full featured yet compact core. It conforms to the ISO 11898-1, CAN 2.0A and CAN 2.0 B Standards. Bits rates of up to 1 Mbps are supported. The core size can be optimized via parameterized configurations for both acceptance filtering and FIFO depth. The full version of the CAN core can be purchased and downloaded from the Xilinx IP Center: http://www.xilinx.com/ipcenter/.
